{"tid":1284790,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日韓貿易戰害到偶像！韓網友要求TWICE、IZ*ONE成員退團","createTime":"2019-07-04T10:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T23:23:28.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"44d3787b8e427089a8e06b164fbff7a017223d93","tid":1284790,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:16:47.000Z","msg":"原本只是兩國政治與經濟問題，現在卻影響到了演藝圈！日本近日放話要對南韓「出口管制」，使得韓國人開始抵制、呼籲拒買日本貨，而現在偶像團體也遭殃，目前正當紅的兩個女團TWICE跟IZ*ONE，裡面都各有3位日本成員，遭韓網友要求退出團體！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4212/d4212258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4212%2Fd4212258.jpg&h=7ec900a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日韓貿易戰害到偶像！韓網友要求TWICE、IZ*ONE成員退團。（圖／翻攝自TWICE、IZ*ONE臉書）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE近年在日本發展成績斐然，只要在日本活動，可以藉著MOMO（平井桃）、Sana（湊崎紗夏）和Mina（名井南）的日文能力暢行無阻，打下日本市場可說是不可或缺的功臣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4212/d4212271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4212%2Fd4212271.jpg&h=4f70330e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE日籍成員MOMO、SANA、MINA。（圖／翻攝自TWICE臉書）<br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE是南韓電視台與AKB48合作的選秀節目《Produce 48》，去年所選拔出的日韓限定女團，雖然最終日籍成員沒有想像得多，但宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子與本田仁美都擁有超高人氣，日前來台開唱，在台灣與海外也累積不少死忠粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n由於日韓爆發貿易戰，偶像團體意外中槍，不僅TWICE、IZ*ONE，包含男團NCT127、PENTAGON等也都有日籍成員，不少網友發起拒看這些團體、拒買該團商品，甚至要求日本成員退團等言論，逐漸在韓網延燒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4212/d4212281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4212%2Fd4212281.jpg&h=90c9fcdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IZ*ONE日籍成員宮脇咲良、矢吹奈子與本田仁美。（圖／翻攝自IZ*ONE臉書）<br />\n<br />\n日本政府1日宣布將對南韓實施嚴格的半導體出口限制，等於控管出口到南韓的相關原料。對此，南韓企劃財政部長洪楠基4日也回應，若日本真的實施長期限制，南韓也會採取反制措施。不僅偶像團體，南韓網友也發起拒買日本商品，如Uniqlo、SK2、資生堂、7-Eleven、日本3C品牌等抵制活動。<br />\n<br />\n支持釘升物仙MOMO退團SOLO"},{"pid":"329879a6baa9aeb9242f82cf054535927417ea62","tid":1284790,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"Momo人間性器都反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9079f27aec29569c91e337223a361566088b261","tid":1284790,"uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":19,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"329879a6baa9aeb9242f82cf054535927417ea62","tid":1284790,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"Momo人間性器都反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"一直支持TWICE三寶下海"},{"pid":"a8946b11c0e12339dd1bb07b5b7e2b21311f3f68","tid":1284790,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"d9079f27aec29569c91e337223a361566088b261","tid":1284790,"uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":19,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"329879a6baa9aeb9242f82cf054535927417ea62","tid":1284790,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"Momo人間性器都反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"一直支持TWICE三寶下海"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"係幾淫 但要尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你身為kpop界一哥要比番面once"},{"pid":"44653dfdd7864bcaa93f58bfd123e9946b57d2ca","tid":1284790,"uid":74065,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"a8946b11c0e12339dd1bb07b5b7e2b21311f3f68","tid":1284790,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"d9079f27aec29569c91e337223a361566088b261","tid":1284790,"uid":74065,"like":9,"dislike":19,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"329879a6baa9aeb9242f82cf054535927417ea62","tid":1284790,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"Momo人間性器都反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"一直支持TWICE三寶下海"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"係幾淫 但要尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /